file.name: auth-scheme.yaml
file.content:
openapi: "3.0.0"
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: Auth Scheme
paths:
  /user:
    get:
      summary: View the current User
      security:
        - basic: []
      responses:
        '200':
          description: An user
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: string
components:
  securitySchemes:
    basic:
      type: http
      scheme: basic
